OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773997500
OL,3,CHealth Secretary urges more people to
OL,4,Cget vaccinated amid meningitis outbreak
OL,6,FThe Health Secretary has expanded his
OL,7,Fappeal to more people to get
OL,8,Fantibiotics or the vaccine for
OL,9,Fmeningitis after a deadly outbreak of
OL,10,Fthe infection.
OL,12,FThe University of Kent said 600
OL,13,Fmeningitis B (menB) vaccines had been
OL,14,Fadministered on Wednesday, after
OL,15,Fhundreds of students joined a queue
OL,16,Foutside the campus sports centre.
OL,18,FWes Streeting met staff administering
OL,19,Fthe jabs at the vaccination centre at
OL,20,Fthe University of Kent's Canterbury
OL,21,Fcampus.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
