OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773997500
OL,3,CHealth Secretary urges more people to
OL,4,Cget vaccinated amid meningitis outbreak
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian, Mr Streeting
OL,7,Fsaid: "Today I am announcing a further
OL,8,Fexpansion, so anyone who was at Club
OL,9,FChemistry from 5 March onwards, should
OL,10,Fnow come forward for both antibiotics
OL,11,Fand vaccine.
OL,13,F"And anyone who was offered
OL,14,Fantibiotics previously, should now
OL,15,Fcome forward.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773997500
OL,3,CHealth Secretary urges more people to
OL,4,Cget vaccinated amid meningitis outbreak
OL,6,F"That will include more students at
OL,7,Fthe University of Kent and some
OL,8,Fstudents at Canterbury Christchurch
OL,9,FUniversity and six former schools
OL,10,Fwhere we've got known or suspected
OL,11,Fcases."
OL,13,FAbout 5,000 students from the
OL,14,FCanterbury campus of the University of
OL,15,FKent are being offered the jab,
OL,16,Falongside courses of antibiotics.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773997500
OL,3,CHealth Secretary urges more people to
OL,4,Cget vaccinated amid meningitis outbreak
OL,6,FThose who have received it will need
OL,7,Fto return for their second dose after
OL,8,Fa minimum of four weeks, while 6,500
OL,9,Fantibiotics have been given out as a
OL,10,Fprecaution, the university said.
OL,12,FAsked about potential risk to the
OL,13,Fwider public, Mr Streeting said the
OL,14,Foutbreak of meningitis "isn't like
OL,15,FCovid", adding the risk to the general
OL,16,Fpublic is "extremely low".
OL,26,@vD@XOUwD@FO]xD@KOUxD@YO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773997500
OL,3,CHealth Secretary urges more people to
OL,4,Cget vaccinated amid meningitis outbreak
OL,6,F"I really hope actually that people in
OL,7,FCanterbury who would be understandably
OL,8,Fmore anxious than perhaps the rest of
OL,9,Fthe country are reassured by the fact
OL,10,Fthat the transmission of this disease
OL,11,Fis through close personal contact only
OL,12,Fand that's why we've been so concerned
OL,13,Fabout the outbreak around Club
OL,14,FChemistry," he added.
OL,16,F"We've got an effective treatment in
OL,17,Fthe antibiotics, we've got the vaccine
OL,18,Fbeing rolled out, we've done the
OL,19,Fcontact tracing, all of those things
OL,20,Fmean that the risk to the general
OL,21,Fpublic here in Canterbury is low.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773997500
OL,3,CHealth Secretary urges more people to
OL,4,Cget vaccinated amid meningitis outbreak
OL,6,F"I've been here today, I stopped for a
OL,7,Fcoffee in town before coming along to
OL,8,Fthe vaccination centre on the way in
OL,9,Fthis morning.
OL,11,F"People should continue to go about
OL,12,Ftheir lives as normal here in
OL,13,FCanterbury and I hope people take
OL,14,Freassurance for that.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773997500
OL,3,CHealth Secretary urges more people to
OL,4,Cget vaccinated amid meningitis outbreak
OL,6,F"As for the general public, we'd
OL,7,Fexpect to see around 350 cases a year
OL,8,Facross the country so what I'd say to
OL,9,Fpeople in terms of the coming days, in
OL,10,Fterms of what we can expect to see,
OL,11,FI'd expect the numbers related to the
OL,12,Foutbreak here in Canterbury to
OL,13,Fincrease in the coming days.
OL,15,FIt comes as Morrisons confirmed an
OL,16,Femployee who attended Club Chemistry
OL,17,Fhas contracted meningitis.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773997500
OL,3,CHealth Secretary urges more people to
OL,4,Cget vaccinated amid meningitis outbreak
OL,6,FA Morrisons spokesperson said: "We can
OL,7,Fconfirm that a colleague at our
OL,8,FSittingbourne distribution centre
OL,9,Fvisited Club Chemistry and
OL,10,Fsubsequently contracted meningitis.
OL,12,F"He is currently receiving treatment
OL,13,Fand we are in close touch with his
OL,14,Ffamily.
OL,16,F"We are following all government
OL,17,Fguidance, the site is operating as
OL,18,Fnormal and we are continuing to
OL,19,Fmonitor the situation closely."
OL,26,@nD@`OUtD@AOUxD@AOU{D@_O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/16
