OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773997500
OL,3,CHealth Secretary urges more people to
OL,4,Cget vaccinated amid meningitis outbreak
OL,6,FElsewhere, a Kent University student
OL,7,Fsaid three people with meningitis are
OL,8,Fmembers of the cheerleading society
OL,9,Fthere.
OL,11,FOlivia Parkins, 18, who is part of the
OL,12,Fcheerleading society at the University
OL,13,Fof Kent, told the Press Association
OL,14,Fthere have been three confirmed cases
OL,15,Fwithin the society - all of whom are
OL,16,Fin hospital.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773997500
OL,3,CHealth Secretary urges more people to
OL,4,Cget vaccinated amid meningitis outbreak
OL,6,FOne school pupil and one university
OL,7,Fstudent have died and 18 more cases
OL,8,Fwere being investigated by the UK
OL,9,FHealth Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,10,Ffollowing an outbreak of meningitis
OL,11,Flinked to a nightclub in Canterbury.
OL,13,FThe UKHSA issued an alert for the NHS
OL,14,Facross England on Wednesday on signs
OL,15,Fand symptoms of meningitis to look out
OL,16,Ffor, though this does not signal the
OL,17,Foutbreak is going to spread nationwide.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773997500
OL,3,CHealth Secretary urges more people to
OL,4,Cget vaccinated amid meningitis outbreak
OL,6,FThe alert said the illness being seen
OL,7,Fin the Kent outbreak "has been severe
OL,8,Fwith rapid deterioration" and urges
OL,9,Fclinical staff to take infection
OL,10,Fcontrol measures in the period before
OL,11,Fpatients are put on antibiotics, such
OL,12,Fas face masks and other personal
OL,13,Fprotective equipment (PPE).
OL,15,FIt urges doctors to have a "high index
OL,16,Fof suspicion where a young person aged
OL,17,F16 to 30 attends with consistent signs
OL,18,For symptoms" of the bug.
OL,26,@oD@VOUpD@YO]wD@\OUzD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773997500
OL,3,CHealth Secretary urges more people to
OL,4,Cget vaccinated amid meningitis outbreak
OL,6,FStudents from the university halls in
OL,7,FCanterbury who have already left
OL,8,Fcampus will be able to get a menB jab
OL,9,Ffrom their GP, according to the
OL,10,FDepartment of Health.
OL,12,FFive new cases of meningitis were
OL,13,Fannounced by the UKHSA on Wednesday
OL,14,Fmorning, taking the total number being
OL,15,Finvestigated by health officials to 20.
OL,17,FOf these, nine cases have been
OL,18,Fconfirmed in the lab and 11 remain
OL,19,Funder investigation.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773997500
OL,3,CHealth Secretary urges more people to
OL,4,Cget vaccinated amid meningitis outbreak
OL,6,FSix of the confirmed cases have been
OL,7,Fconfirmed as the menB strain.
OL,9,FCanterbury Christ Church University,
OL,10,Falso in Kent, confirmed a meningitis
OL,11,Fcase among its students on Wednesday,
OL,12,Fmeaning confirmed or suspected cases
OL,13,Fhave been reported at two universities
OL,14,Fand five schools.
OL,16,FGPs across the country have also been
OL,17,Ftold to prescribe antibiotics to
OL,18,Fanyone who visited Club Chemistry in
OL,19,FCanterbury from March 5-7, plus
OL,20,Fstudents from the University of Kent.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773997500
OL,3,CHealth Secretary urges more people to
OL,4,Cget vaccinated amid meningitis outbreak
OL,6,FThis is to ensure anyone who has left
OL,7,Fcampus can make sure they get the
OL,8,Fright treatment.
OL,10,FThe number of cases is expected to
OL,11,Frise because the incubation period for
OL,12,Fthe infection to when symptoms appear
OL,13,Fis between two and 14 days.
OL,15,FThe UKHSA stressed there are plenty of
OL,16,FNHS stocks of menB vaccines after
OL,17,Fpharmacies reported they were
OL,18,Fstruggling to obtain stock for people
OL,19,Fwho want to pay privately.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G14/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41815
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773997500
OL,3,CHealth Secretary urges more people to
OL,4,Cget vaccinated amid meningitis outbreak
OL,6,FAll reported cases so far have a link
OL,7,Fto Kent, according to the UKHSA.
OL,9,FMeanwhile, French authorities said a
OL,10,Fperson who was admitted to hospital
OL,11,Fwith meningitis in France with links
OL,12,Fto the Kent outbreak is now in a
OL,13,F"stable" condition.
OL,15,FThe French ministry of health told the
OL,16,FPress Association no other cases of
OL,17,Fmeningitis linked to the outbreak in
OL,18,FKent have been reported in France.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G15/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
